🧩 D. Investor & Modal Injection System — (Final, copy-paste ready)  
  
Tujuan: sediakan jalur aman & audit-able supaya investor bisa menyuntikkan modal ke proyek / brankas / wallet mereka sendiri — baik off-chain (bank/VA) atau on-chain (crypto). Seluruh flow terintegrasi ke Multisig + Rivest voting + Vault.  
  
  
---  
  
1) Data model (tambahan)  
  
Investor (userId FK, investor_code, verified:boolean, profileMeta:JSON)  
  
InvestorDeposit (id, investorId, amount, currency, source:'fiat'|'crypto', status, txRef, meta)  
  
ProjectFund (id, projectId, amountAllocated, sourceDepositId)  
  
DepositWebhookLog (id, provider, payload, status)  
  
  
> Tambah file models: Investor.js, InvestorDeposit.js, ProjectFund.js, DepositWebhookLog.js.  
  
  
  
  
---  
  
2) Routes & Controllers (backend/routes/investor.js)  
  
POST /api/investor/deposit/init → buat deposit record, return instruksi pembayaran (VA / onchain addr / external link).  
  
POST /api/investor/deposit/verify → webhook/callback dari gateway; verifikasi signature, update deposit -> success, credit investor wallet.  
  
GET /api/investor/deposits → list deposit history (auth).  
  
POST /api/investor/project/allocate → alokasikan deposit ke project (requires multisig if > threshold).  
  
  
Controllers harus:  
  
1. validasi input  
  
  
2. buat InvestorDeposit dengan status=pending  
  
  
3. generate txRef unik (sha256(user|ts|random))  
  
  
4. jika fiat → return VA/payment link; jika crypto → return onchain address + memo  
  
  
5. pada verify → atomic DB transaction: credit Wallet, create Transaction row, create VaultEvent jika pemindahan ke brankas.  
  
  
  
  
---  
  
3) Multisig + Approval Logic  
  
Jika alokasi ke ProjectFund melebihi THRESHOLD_ALLOCATION (env), buat MultisigRequest otomatis dengan purpose: allocate_project_x.  
  
Keluarkan notifikasi ke room VIP + email investor (opsional).  
  
Vote via services/multisigService.voteMultisig — saat approvals >= required → executed → panggil vaultManagerService.executeAllocation.  
  
  
  
---  
  
4) Frontend (Investor Dashboard)  
  
Halaman: /investor — tampilkan: deposit init form (amount, currency, method), riwayat deposit, project allocation UI.  
  
Flow cepat: user klik deposit → pilih method → show instruksi (VA / onchain) + tombol I HAVE PAID untuk manual confirm.  
  
Tampilkan status webhook realtime (pending → success) via socket event depositUpdate.  
  
  
  
---  
  
5) Security & Compliance  
  
Simpan minimal metadata (no raw payment credentials).  
  
Untuk fiat: simpan receipt hash & webhook log (tidak menyimpan file gambar secara langsung — simpan s3 ref).  
  
Rate-limit endpoint deposit/init untuk mencegah spam.  
  
Wajibkan KYC minimal untuk investor sebelum deposit > X (env KYC_THRESHOLD).  
  
  
  
---  
  
6) Env variables  
  
DEPOSIT_ONCHAIN_ADDR=...  
DEPOSIT_FIAT_PROVIDER_URL=...  
THRESHOLD_ALLOCATION=10000  
KYC_THRESHOLD=500  
  
  
